parameters:
\nc<>(Wow, that camera looks expensive and it even has
soundproofing...)
(It's more professional than I
thought.)
\nc<>(They said I would be buried, but I agreed anyway...)

\nc<>(W-What should I do? I have to speak in front of all those
people...)
\nc<>(Just imagining it makes me want to puke... ugh...)

\nc<>Nice to meet everyone who came here seeking a popular muscle
life! I'm Matsuo-kun from Matsuo Fitness!

\nc<>Isn't it sweaty and stuffy to always have muscular guys on
the screen?

\nc<>So today, we have invited a special guest. Yes, please give
your greetings!

\nc<>Thank you very much for agreeing to collaborate on today's
livestream! I will do my best...

\nc<>Ha! I said it's fine, no need to be so formal even though
we're both streamers. Are you nervous?

\nc<>Don't worry. This time's livestream is structured to move
our bodies rather than just talking.

\nc<>Just being a magical girl is enough to pique everyone's
interest.
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[0]デュフチューブで初めて見た");
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[0]今日からファンになります");
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[0]レヴァンティア聞いたことあるぞ");
\nc<>I'm not self-proclaimed, you know!? I'm an adult woman...

\nc<>That's correct, but...! I also like being called a
girl...!
\nc<>That's right, it's better to be a little more assertive.

\nc<>Alright, let's begin! Today's content is... Shura vs.
Rasetsu! A showdown between magical girls and physical
strength!

\nc<>First, let's start with 100 push-ups!! If all the listeners
can keep up, give it a try! 1, 2!!
\nc<>Keep it up! *huff* *huff* Now, let's move on to 100 squats!

\nc<>(Well, if it's Levantia's physical abilities, it should be
easy.)

\nc<>(Somehow, it feels like my chest and butt have been getting
more attention lately...)

\nc<>(...It's just my imagination, right?) (I'm just exercising
normally.)

\nc<>Haa, haa! Not even a single drop of sweat, as expected of a
magical girl!
\nc<>Ahaha... I think Matsuo-san, who is keeping up, is amazing.
\nc<>Nuuu! I can't lose if you say something like that!

\nc<>It's bad, Levantia! A villain has appeared in the city,
please come and help meow!

\nc<>Huh? Hey, where are you going? We're in the middle of a
live shoot, hey!
\nc<>S-Sorry! I have to go help someone...!
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[0]おっぱいとおしり揺れるの");

\nc<>Hold on, hold on, hold on! I didn't say anything about
pulling out!
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[0]見に来たら誰もいませんね");
